        <item>
            <title>iPhone 16 爆假機事件，先達回收商蝕 3 萬指生意難捱</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-16-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 05:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1264676</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPhone 16 系列日前正式開賣，先達廣場內發生回收商收到假機的騙案，令其中一家店損失了高達 3 萬元。涉事店家指出，這是開賣首日便發生的事件，回收的兩部 iPhone 16 Pro Max 外觀與真機極為相似，連盒內配件都非常完整，令店主慨嘆「生意難做」。</p><p>一名店主在 Facebook 上分享了這宗騙案的詳情，並附上假機的照片，兩部手機的包裝盒、配件及手機的外觀都與真機幾乎無異，難以分辨。這次事件令得主感到無奈，並表示手機市場的詐騙手法日益高明，回收商需更加謹慎。</p><p>據瞭解，該事件發生於旺角先達廣場一間回收商店內。該店主表示，事發時因店舖人多擁擠，工作繁忙，未能即時仔細檢查，導致收到兩部假機，隨後發現損失高達 3 萬元。涉事店鋪已立即報警處理。</p><p>警方接獲報案後，根據初步調查結果，將案件列為「以欺騙手段取得財產」，並交由旺角刑事調查隊第二隊跟進調查。據悉，報案人稱早前在西洋菜南街的另一商場內，以 24,000 元購入兩部手機，並在亞皆老街另一商場打算轉售時發現它們是樣辦機。至今警方尚未拘捕涉案人士，案件仍在調查中。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649-641x580.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649-641x580.jpg 641w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649.jpg 994w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 641px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460722730_9202849267-435x580.j